headline: We Battled Big Food. Can RFK, Jr. Succeed Where We Failed?
summary: Two former top health officials say Kennedy can Make America Healthy Again—if he’s willing to take on soda companies, ultraprocessed foods, farm subsidies and other powerful forces that shape the way we eat.
